	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I did this quest in its entirety and it was a lot of fun, a major step up from all those stupid &quot;get some bat wings&quot; newbie quests.  The info presented here was great.  A few notes though:<BR>
<BR>
1.  If you're not going by ports, at least try and bring a sower along, there's a lot of running involved.<BR>
2.  The only stuff you have to do in order is the npc's who you talk to for the bag.<BR>
3.  Definitely have a group in the unrest, or if you have a high lvl druid friend with wolf form, get them to help you with the pulls.  I didn't find squat off the normal ghouls, so we had to pull crazed and carrion ghouls of the second floor.  Scary stuff up there.<BR>
4.  In the high keep just ask around instead of trying to kill for the scroll yourself.  Since there's no other use for it people will likely be willing to point you in the direction of a slain gob that has it.<BR>
5.  As for the crazed goblins, (which are in BB), be careful.  The hit hard.  I, at 24, was only able to pull this off with the help of some lvl 30's (who made it rather easy).  And we camped it for a few hours one night finding nothing, only to have the blade drop first kill on the next day.  So you might have to wait a while, but at least its good exp.<BR>
6.  As for the skellies in Najena, be careful if you're lower than 23 or so as that crap will likely agro you.  I walked in there (at lvl 24) with no problems, the only things that agroed being a spider and the mobs that you have to kill for the hilt.<BR>
7.  The npc outside the unrest was not on the stone pillar at the time I found her.  She was on the hill to the left of the unrest enterance.  So check both places.<BR>
8.  You might have some trouble with Kanthuk ogrebane.  You'll probably have to try several different tacts when talking to him, but eventually he gives up the ammy if you can figure out what he wants you to say.<BR>
<BR>
Steelborn Brellson<BR>
25 Paladin of Brell<BR>
Bertox server
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
